{"tid":1428813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"七月十四記得燒街衣","createTime":"2019-08-07T11:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T11:06:44.000Z","uid":295150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7e6239765dc4b3477fb4318131657caec678a159","tid":1428813,"uid":295150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:06:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.discoverhongkong.com/tc/events-festivals/other-festivals/the-hungry-ghost-festival.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.discoverhongkong.com%2Ftc%2Fevents-festivals%2Fother-festivals%2Fthe-hungry-ghost-festival.jsp&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=35fdc72c\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.discoverhongkong.com/tc/events-festivals/other-festivals/the-hungry-ghost-festival.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n香港潮人盂蘭勝會<br />\n香港的潮籍人士約有120多萬，過去他們從中國內地移居到港時帶來了盂蘭勝會的傳統，至今已有百多年歷史。他們所辦的盂蘭勝會，從農曆七月初一舉行，一直到七月底，活動包括祭祀、燒紙錢、派平安米、福物競投、神功戲演出等。2011年，香港潮人盂蘭勝會更被列入第三批《國家級非物質文化遺產名錄》中。<br />\n<br />\n西曆2019年8月15日<br />\n吉時：晚上6點-11點<br />\n孝順下阿爺阿嫲阿公阿婆齊齊陪佢地落街燒衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}